<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<title>San Antonio Coding Challenge | How You Can Help</title>
	<%- include partials/meta.ejs %>
	<meta name="description" content="Learn how you can help keep the San Antonio Coding Challenge running smoothly.">
</head>

<body>

	<%- include partials/ga.ejs %>
	<%- include partials/nav.ejs %>

	<div class="jumbotron">
		<div class="content container">
			<h1>how you can help</h1>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="container help">

		<div class="ui cards">

			<div class="ui card">
				<div class="content icon">
					<span class="fa-stack fa-5x">
			  			<i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i>
			  			<i class="fa fa-usd fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="content header">
					<h3>{become a sponsor}</h3>
				</div>
				<div class="content">
					<p>You can sponsor one or more of the events with monetary or in-kind donations. To see the different sponsorship levels you can visit our <a href="sponsors">sponsors</a> page</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="ui card">
				<div class="content icon">
					<span class="fa-stack fa-5x">
			  			<i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i>
			  			<i class="fa fa-users fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="content header">
					<h3>{volunteer}</h3>
				</div>
				<div class="content">
					<p>We need volunteers for the following -</p>
					<ul>
						<li>food preparation</li>
						<li>registering attendance</li>
						<li>scoring the challenges</li>
						<li>setting up</li>
						<li>web site maintenance (see our <a href="https://github.com/sacodingchallenge" target="_blank">Github</a>)</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="ui card">
				<div class="content icon">
					<span class="fa-stack fa-5x">
			  			<i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i>
			  			<i class="fa fa-share-alt fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="content header">
					<h3>{promote}</h3>
				</div>
				<div class="content">
					<p>You can help us promote our events by:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>pushing your Coding Challenge solutions to <a href="https://github.com/greenlightchallenges/codingchallenges" target="_blank">the repo</a></li>
						<li>sharing on social media (links below)</li>
						<li>displaying our <a href="70s.pdf" target="_blank">flyers</a> in your workplace</li>
						<li>word of mouth</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>

	</div>	

	<%- include partials/footer.ejs %>